China to Develop Nuclear Power to Help Cut Emissions, Xie Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-22T01:20:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/china-to-develop-nuclear-power-to-help-cut-emissions-xie-says.html
China  will continue to develop
nuclear power to help reduce carbon emissions, Xie Zhenhua, vice
chairman of the National Development and Reform Commission, told
a conference in Beijing today. China will develop atomic energy
in a safe manner, Xie said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chua Baizhen in Beijing at 
